<p>May the memories you hold dear bring you comfort and strength during this time of sorrow. May the love and support of those around you ease your pain and help you find peace.  Remember that grief is a journey, and it’s okay to feel whatever emotions arise.  Take your time, allow yourself to heal, and know that your loved one will always be remembered and cherished.  With time, may you find solace and a renewed sense of hope, embracing the beautiful legacy they have left behind.  Peace be with you.</p>
    
  
